35:47.755 --> 35:51.202
<i>I know morning will come</i>

35:51.258 --> 35:55.206
<i>But pardon my laughter</i>

35:56.163 --> 36:00.703
<i>In each scenario
you can depend on the end</i>

36:00.768 --> 36:04.306
<i>Where the lovers agree</i>

