<i>To come through with air mail</i>

44:50.664 --> 44:53.406
<i>The dancing crowds</i>

44:53.466 --> 44:55.912
<i>Look up to some rare male</i>

44:55.969 --> 44:57.471
<i>Like that Astaire male</i>

44:57.537 --> 45:00.040
<i>See the pretty ladies, top of the crop</i>

45:00.106 --> 45:03.315
<i>You wanna know the way the wind blows?</i>

