53:27.613 --> 53:30.025
I'm glad I don't have to clean it.

53:30.083 --> 53:32.825
"It's the mother of Parliaments
dedicated to the right of..."

53:32.885 --> 53:35.297
Holy smoke! That reminds me.
I forgot to write my mother.

53:35.354 --> 53:36.492
Come on, let's go, Eddie.

