58:50.002 --> 58:52.482
<i>After all the dizzy excitement
of our first show abroad,</i>

58:52.538 --> 58:54.609
<i>the trip home was a letdown.</i>

58:54.673 --> 58:57.119
<i>And once again Larry became restless.</i>

