59:16.529 --> 59:19.703
Ship to shore. What are you waiting for?

59:22.468 --> 59:24.607
Hello! Hello!

59:26.205 --> 59:28.207
Well, aren't you excited?

59:28.707 --> 59:32.086
Oh. Well, tomorrow morning.

59:33.446 --> 59:35.392
I'll meet you at the dock.

59:35.448 --> 59:38.554
